snippet.title: Winzer gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Winzer, Dos PC game produced by Starbyte Software in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/winzer/831/
Exploring the interface in this unusual wine-based business simulation.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
